    Title: Adi Granth
Tags:
  - Invocation=Fusion
  - Invocation=The Dispeller of Sin
---
Thou, Hari, knowest and pervadest all. Murmur, O soul, the Name of Hari, and
sins will disappear. Thou art I and I am Thou, and there is no difference;
such is gold and bracelet, water and wave.
